text: Farid Zizi is a French aerospace engineer. Since 1 August 2018, he has been the head of the France Aviation Civile Services (previously DSNA Services).Farid Zizi prend la direction de DSNA Services He is known for having been head of the Education and Research at the French Civil Aviation UniversityEnac.
